# Styling rules

## Design tokens

- **Hex colors only** in `src/style.css` (`:root` for light, `.dark` for dark)
- Map tokens to Tailwind via `@theme inline` (`--color-background`, etc.)
- In components use semantic classes: `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground`, `border-border`, `bg-card`

## Tailwind v4

- Main entry: `@import "tailwindcss"` in `src/style.css`
- Dark mode: class on `<html>` — `@custom-variant dark (&:is(.dark *))`
- Prefer utilities over custom CSS in Vue files
- **No arbitrary sizes** — use scale tokens instead of `[Xrem]` / `[Xpx]` brackets:
  - `h-[24rem]` → `h-96`, `w-[24rem]` → `w-96`, both → `size-96`
  - `h-[28rem]` → `h-112`, `w-[28rem]` → `w-112`, both → `size-112`
  - When `h-*` and `w-*` match, collapse into `size-*`

## Layout container

- Use `container` utility for section/page wrappers — **never** `mx-auto px-4 md:px-6`
- `container` is defined in `src/style.css` via `@utility`: sets `margin-inline: auto`, `padding-inline: 1rem`
- **No additional `max-w-*`** alongside `container` — max-width is already baked in

```html
<!-- ❌ BAD -->
<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 md:px-6">

<!-- ✅ GOOD -->
<div class="container">
```

## Shared utilities (style.css)

- `.glass-card` — glass surface
- `.text-gradient` — accent gradient text
- `.bg-grid` — subtle dot grid
- `.cta-glow` — primary CTA glow
- `.fade-up` / `.fade-up.is-visible` — scroll reveal

## Component styling

- Reuse `GlassCard`, `SectionHeading`, `TechTag` before inventing new patterns
- **Light and dark parity** required for every new component
- `@apply` only inside `src/style.css` `@layer base` when needed

## Motion

- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion: reduce`
- No parallax, no heavy 3D, no aggressive neon animations

## Formatting

- Prettier with `prettier-plugin-tailwindcss`, `prettier-plugin-classnames`, `prettier-plugin-merge` (merge **last**)
